{"tha-ap164:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap164:0.2":"Suparicariyavagga ","tha-ap164:0.3":"Kanaverapupphiyattheraapadana ","tha-ap164:1.1":"“Siddhattho nama bhagava, ","tha-ap164:1.2":"lokajettho narasabho; ","tha-ap164:1.3":"Purakkhato savakehi, ","tha-ap164:1.4":"nagaram patipajjatha. ","tha-ap164:2.1":"Ranno antepure asim, ","tha-ap164:2.2":"gopako abhisammato; ","tha-ap164:2.3":"Pasade upavitthoham, ","tha-ap164:2.4":"addasam lokanayakam. ","tha-ap164:3.1":"Kanaveram gahetvana, ","tha-ap164:3.2":"bhikkhusanghe samokirim; ","tha-ap164:3.3":"Buddhassa visum katvana, ","tha-ap164:3.4":"tato bhiyyo samokirim. ","tha-ap164:4.1":"Catunnavutito kappe, ","tha-ap164:4.2":"Yam pupphamabhipujayim; ","tha-ap164:4.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap164:4.4":"Buddhapujayidam phalam. ","tha-ap164:5.1":"Sattasitimhito kappe, ","tha-ap164:5.2":"caturasum mahiddhika; ","tha-ap164:5.3":"Sattaratanasampanna, ","tha-ap164:5.4":"cakkavatti mahabbala. ","tha-ap164:6.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap164:6.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap164:6.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap164:7.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma kanaverapupphiyo thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap164:8.1":"Kanaverapupphiyattherassapadanam dutiyam. "}